---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout base="/us" title="How to report scams in the USA" description="Step-by-step guide: stay safe, collect details, and use the right official form to report scams in the United States.">
  <h1>How to report scams in the USA</h1>

  <section>
    <h2>Step 1 – Make sure you are safe</h2>
    <p>Stop all contact with the scammer. Secure your accounts: change passwords, enable two-factor authentication if possible, and alert your bank or card issuer if money or details were shared.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Step 2 – Collect details</h2>
    <p>Gather what you have before reporting:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Dates and times of contact</li>
      <li>Amounts of money involved</li>
      <li>Phone numbers, emails, or URLs used</li>
      <li>Screenshots, emails, or messages</li>
      <li>How you paid (card, wire, crypto, etc.)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Step 3 – Use the right official form</h2>
    <p>Choose the row that best matches your situation and use the official link to report.</p>
    <div class="table-wrap">
      <table class="routing-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Situation</th>
            <th>Where to go (official)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Online scam, phishing, hacked account</td>
            <td><a href="https://www.ic3.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IC3 – FBI internet crime</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Fake business, shopping scam, fraud calls</td>
            <td><a href="https://reportfraud.ftc.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">FTC ReportFraud</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Bank / card / loan problem or scam</td>
            <td><a href="https://www.consumerfinance.gov/complaint/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CFPB complaint</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>IRS or Treasury-looking email / call</td>
            <td><a href="https://www.irs.gov/privacy-disclosure/report-phishing" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IRS phishing</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Problem with a government agency</td>
            <td><a href="https://www.usa.gov/agency-complaints" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">USA.gov agency complaints</a></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Corruption / waste in federal programs</td>
            <td><a href="https://www.oversight.gov/report-fraud-waste-abuse" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Oversight.gov – where to report</a></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p>Not sure where to start? <a href="https://www.usa.gov/where-report-scams" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">USA.gov – Where to report a scam</a> helps you find the right place.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .routing-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .routing-table th,
  .routing-table td {
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    text-align: left;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .routing-table th {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .routing-table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
</style>
